parameters.name: Dimension
parameters.description: The dimensions based on which the resources are queried.

parameters.name: GroupId
parameters.description:
The ID of the application group.

For information about how to query the IDs of application groups, see [DescribeMonitorGroups](~~115032~~).

parameters.name: Md5
parameters.description: The MD5 value of the HTTP request body. The MD5 value is a 128-bit hash value used to verify the uniqueness of the reported monitoring data.

parameters.name: MetricName
parameters.description: The name of the custom metric.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description:
The page number.

Pages start from page 1. Default value: 1.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description:
The number of entries per page.

Pages start from page 1. Default value: 10.
